spec_data.Name: texlive-aspectratio
spec_data.Description:
The package provides fonts (both as Adobe Type 1 format, and as
Metafont source) for the 'AR' symbol (for Aspect Ratio) used by
aeronautical scientists and engineers. Note that the package
supersedes the package ar
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:37:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Capital A and capital R ligature for Aspect Ratio
